{"tid":1289151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"烏魯木齊七五事件10週年 維吾爾族青年回憶血腥鎮壓","createTime":"2019-07-06T03:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T14:42:54.000Z","uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0e1a3013447a3809c84f5c269dd0f97c0050b8bc","tid":1289151,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:25:00.000Z","msg":"10年前的今天，在中國新疆維吾爾族自治區首府烏魯木齊，民眾發起和平示威，抗議在廣東一處工廠工作的兩名維族人，慘遭漢族人打死，要求當局全面調查。警方試圖驅離，結果演變成大規模暴動、血腥鎮壓，約200人喪命，事後許多維族人逃到土耳其生活，而現在回想起來，他們依然心有餘悸。<br />\n<br />\n2009年7月5日在新疆烏魯木齊，上千名維吾爾族人參與和平示威，結果演變成警民流血衝突。<br />\n<br />\n當年只有9歲的阿不都沙拉木，感受到了人生中最驚恐的一瞬間，他回憶「我很害怕，我找不到我父親，我就開始跑，然後兩名可能是特種部隊的成員，我不確定，但是是中國人（漢人）回來找我，對我開槍，子彈正好從我右耳後面過去，我很幸運我還活著」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/1Zl2bp89.YTiUe2jd8m.tw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/ftvn.com.tw/e9727e28604b900ff078f8dfb270bac7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F1Zl2bp89.YTiUe2jd8m.tw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fftvn.com.tw%2Fe9727e28604b900ff078f8dfb270bac7&h=eab031d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歷經了九死一生，阿不都沙拉木和眾多維族人一樣，逃到文化、語言、宗教相似的土耳其，展開新生活。而專家指出，烏魯木齊七五事件成了新疆的轉捩點，北京政府從此對他們態度特別強硬。<br />\n<br />\n現在有數不清的維族人被送到「再教育營」，這個中國當局號稱是要打擊恐怖主義並教導他們一技之長的地方，不過曾被關押的人披露，那根本是用來政治洗腦和心靈折磨的集中營，他們被迫拋棄伊斯蘭信仰、宣誓效忠中國國家主席習近平。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UUyWkoN2YdbkhV20KHPexQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/ftvn.com.tw/a211ba8052d94199feafb80892bf3e2b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUUyWkoN2YdbkhV20KHPexQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fftvn.com.tw%2Fa211ba8052d94199feafb80892bf3e2b&h=d9710faa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿不都沙拉木表示，從2017年6月，他的父親便杳無音訊，去年9月，有在土耳其的熟人告訴阿不都沙拉木，自己遭拘留於再教育營時，看過他的父親。<br />\n<br />\n新疆騷亂一晃眼十年過去了，維吾爾族的處境卻越來越艱辛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%83%8F%E9%AD%AF%E6%9C%A8%E9%BD%8A%E4%B8%83%E4%BA%94%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B610%E9%80%B1%E5%B9%B4-%E7%B6%AD%E5%90%BE%E7%88%BE%E6%97%8F%E5%9B%9E%E6%86%B6%E8%A1%80%E8%85%A5%E9%8E%AE%E5%A3%93-015507116.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2583%258F%25E9%25AD%25AF%25E6%259C%25A8%25E9%25BD%258A%25E4%25B8%2583%25E4%25BA%2594%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B610%25E9%2580%25B1%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E5%2590%25BE%25E7%2588%25BE%25E6%2597%258F%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2586%25B6%25E8%25A1%2580%25E8%2585%25A5%25E9%258E%25AE%25E5%25A3%2593-015507116.html&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjYeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=b73e7a54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%83%8F%E9%AD%AF%E6%9C%A8%E9%BD%8A%E4%B8%83%E4%BA%94%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B610%E9%80%B1%E5%B9%B4-%E7%B6%AD%E5%90%BE%E7%88%BE%E6%97%8F%E5%9B%9E%E6%86%B6%E8%A1%80%E8%85%A5%E9%8E%AE%E5%A3%93-015507116.html</a>"},{"pid":"1e483d534e61f85d4892ddbe7174abd7c10dc213","tid":1289151,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:25:39.000Z","msg":"兒登仔 : 今次就撐中共喇"},{"pid":"6e7a07cd6ee64b681671cd8cc84c763008f8333c","tid":1289151,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb345ea4591fef1d5264dba635961f6a70e09b07","tid":1289151,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/16143531/image1542349924956.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F16143531%2Fimage1542349924956.png&h=b92bc27b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39e5e680092c902b42b562910d6c87aa88b4f6a9","tid":1289151,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":4,"s